T02D3401:66a-1: t'i sa ma ya r'a dza s'a dha nam /
T02D3401:66a-3: dam tshig gsum gyi rgyal po'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3401:66a-4: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3401:66a-5: mi mnyam mi g-yo shin tu yang dag chos kyi snying //
T02D3401:66a-6: snying rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba rnams kyi sdug bsngal 'joms //
T02D3401:66a-7: mnyam med yon tan kun dang dngos grub ster mdzad pa //
T02D3401:66a-8: dri med mi g-yo mtshungs med rab mchog chos rnams ni //
T02D3401:66a-9: nam mkha' dang mtshungs de rnams dpe med yon tan gyi //
T02D3401:66a-10: cha shas rdul phran zegs mas kyang ni mtshams med pa //
T02D3401:66a-11: rtag tu sems can khams byed dngos grub sbyin pa po //
T02D3401:66a-12: dpe dang bral zhing ma lus pa yi dngos grub rnams //
T02D3401:66a-13: rtag tu dri med snying rje'i shugs kyis langs nas ni //
T02D3401:66a-14: smon lam grub cing 'gog pa med pa'i chos nyid do //
T02D3401:66a-15: 'gro ba'i don du sgrub thabs gzhan yang mtha' med pa //
T02D3401:66a-16: brtse ba chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par mdzes //
T02D3401:66a-17: 'gag med snying rje'i spyod pa g-yo ba med pa yis //
T02D3401:66b-0: 'jig rten @66b gsum bgrod mchog gi dngos grub sbyin pa po //
T02D3401:66b-1: gzhal bya gzhal byed dang bral legs par yongs rdzogs shing //
T02D3401:66b-2: kye ma chos nyid der 'jug legs par khong du chud //
T02D3401:66b-3: dam tshig gsum mchog dngos grub mchog sbyin ster mdzad pa //
T02D3401:66b-4: sbyin pa'i mchog de bdag la rtag tu legs par stsol //
T02D3401:66b-5: 'jig rten gsum kun mchog sbyin mchog gi sgrub pa po //
T02D3401:66b-6: mgon po dus gsum gshegs rnams kun nas sgrib med pa //
T02D3401:66b-7: dam tshig gsum rgyal rtog par gsungs //
T02D3401:66b-8: rdor 'dzin glu dang bstod pa bya //
T02D3401:66b-9: de 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
T02D3401:66b-10: yon tan rgya chen phul du byung //
T02D3401:66b-11: lan cig tsam du brjod pas kyang //
T02D3401:66b-12: sngags rnams thams cad nges par 'grub //
T02D3401:66b-13: bstod pa'i rgyal po 'di yis ni //
T02D3401:66b-14: de bzhin gshegs rnams nges par mnyes //
T02D3401:66b-15: dngos grub rgya chen ster bar byed //
T02D3401:66b-16: rtog pa la gnas rtog las gsungs //
T02D3401:66b-17: mgon po rnam par snang mdzad che //
T02D3401:66b-18: mi bskyod rin chen 'byung ldan dang //
T02D3401:66b-19: rgyal ba dag pa 'od dpag med //
T02D3401:66b-20: don yod grub pa rgyal po kun //
T02D3401:66b-21: ro dang ro bcud de nyid dang //
T02D3401:66b-22: mchog tu ster bar mdzad pa ste //
T02D3401:66b-23: ma lus dngos grub dag dang ni //
T02D3401:66b-24: dga' ba rgya chen phun tshogs gnas //
T02D3401:66b-25: bsam pa thams cad yongs su gang //
T02D3401:66b-26: yid kyi 'dod pa yongs su ster //
T02D3401:66b-27: ye shes tshe dang stobs kyi shugs //
T02D3401:66b-28: dge ba'i mchog rnams ster ba po //
T02D3401:66b-30: de bzhin du bstod pa 'di rdo rje'i gur gyis brgyan pa /
T02D3401:66b-31: rnal 'byor rgyud chen po'i rjes su 'brang nas brjod par bya'o zhes so //
T02D3401:66b-32: sangs rgyas kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3401:66b-33: sangs rgyas sras kyi rang bzhin dang //
T02D3401:66b-34: dus gsum sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal nas //
T02D3401:66b-36: dpal ldan dam tshig gsum las gsungs //
T02D3401:66b-37: dam chos smad par mi bya zhing //
T02D3401:66b-38: gang du'ang spang bar mi bya'o //
T02D3401:66b-39: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems //
T02D3401:66b-40: de rnams mi gus spang bar bya //
T02D3401:66b-41: bla ma'i bka' las 'da' mi bya //
T02D3401:66b-42: lus can rnams ni gsad mi bya //
T02D3401:66b-43: rang gi sngags dang phyag rgya yang //
T02D3401:66b-44: don med pa dang nyams mi bya //
T02D3401:66b-45: ser sna chang gi btung ba ni //
T02D3401:66b-46: thams cad du yang bya ba min //
T02D3401:66b-47: rdo rje'i rnam pa mi 'gong zhing //
T02D3401:66b-48: bza' bar bya ba'ang ma yin no //
T02D3401:67a-2: phyag rgya mi gus spang bar bya //
T02D3401:67a-3: bla ma dang ni lha rnams drung //
T02D3401:67a-4: byis pa'i chos nyid mi bya'o //
T02D3401:67a-5: mngon spyod bya ba ma yin zhing //
T02D3401:67a-6: tshul khrims ldan pa smad mi bya //
T02D3401:67a-7: bya min bya ba mi bya zhing //
T02D3401:67a-8: sdig la rjes su yi rang min //
T02D3401:67a-9: rang gzhan rjes su mi mthun pa'i//
T02D3401:67a-10: bya ba rnams ni spang bar bya //
T02D3401:67a-11: rtog pa chen po'i dam tshig 'di //
T02D3401:67a-12: dpal ldan dam tshig gsum las shes //
T02D3401:67a-14: tshogs smra dga' bas chog par bya //
T02D3401:67a-15: the tshom nyid du gyur pa dang //
T02D3401:67a-16: yo byad yongs su 'dzin pa dang //
T02D3401:67a-17: le lo dang ni zhum pa'i sems //
T02D3401:67a-18: de bzhin bdag la bstod la sogs //
T02D3401:67a-19: bar du gcod pa'i chos rnams su //
T02D3401:67a-20: rtog pa'i rgyal po nyid las gsungs //
T02D3401:67a-21: nyes pa 'di rnams las nges par grol zhing sngon
T02D3401:67a-22: du gsungs pa'i dam tshig la gnas nas chags pa
T02D3401:67a-24: dad pa dang brtan pa'i yang dag pa'i byang chub
T02D3401:67a-25: kyi sems kyis 'gro ba gsum po la phan pa
T02D3401:67a-27: ngag dang yid rnams kyis byed pa dang /
T02D3401:67a-28: dam tshig gsum las gsungs pa'i sgrub thabs kyi cho gas 'dod pa'i dngos grub tu 'gyur ro //
T02D3401:67a-29: rin chen 'byung gnas sbas ba'i zhabs kyis mdzad pa /
